article.description: — George Papas posted 18 points as Monmouth topped Siena 71-59 on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Papas scores 18 to lead Monmouth over Siena 71-59
article.linkText: Papas scores 18 to lead Monmouth over Siena 71-59
article.story: WEST LONG BRANCH, N.J. -- — George Papas posted 18 points as Monmouth topped Siena 71-59 on Tuesday night. Walker Miller had 15 points and seven rebounds for Monmouth (18-9, 10-6 Metro Atlantic Athletic Conference). Shavar Reynolds Jr. added 12 points. Nikkei Rutty had 19 rebounds and four blocks. Jackson Stormo had 16 points and nine rebounds for the Saints (13-11, 10-6). Anthony Gaines added six points and 11 rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
